data.description: This beautiful home is nestled in the heart of Trapp Ky. It is minutes from a locally owned restaurant. It has a full finished basement and a very large deck for entertaining or enjoying the beautiful view. The owner built it himself. The back yard has been known to have deer and turkey come around. Heat and air 1 year old. Roof is 7 years old.
